{
  "title": "如何自行更改Vim配色",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">主要有两种方式安装colorscheme：</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; list-style: none; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 0px 32px; list-style-type: disc; word-break: break-all;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">自行下载colorscheme安装，下载的文件扩展名通常为.vim。</p></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 0px 32px; list-style-type: disc; word-break: break-all;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">通过安装相关vim的插件获取。</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"自行下载colorscheme安装\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a name=\"t0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>自行下载colorscheme安装</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">以mac为例，在系统自带的vim中有个colors文件夹，里面存放的便是各种colorscheme：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/CCC34D23A3754E170554C93E79358D47.png\" alt=\"colors\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; word-break: break-all; cursor: zoom-in;\" width=\"872\" height=\"76\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在vim的配置文件<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">.vimrc</code>中配色方案的设置<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">colorscheme foo</code>为：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" name=\"code\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 8px 16px 4px 56px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; position: relative; overflow-y: hidden; overflow-x: auto; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border: none; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2;\"><code class=\"language-vim hljs bash has-numbering\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; display: block; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; overflow-x: auto; word-wrap: normal; word-break: break-all;\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 136); word-break: break-all;\">set</span> t_Co=<span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 102, 102); word-break: break-all;\">256</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 153, 0); word-break: break-all;\">\" required\ncolorscheme desert</span></code><ul class=\"pre-numbering\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; word-break: break-all; position: absolute; width: 48px; background-color: rgb(238, 240, 244); top: 0px; left: 0px; text-align: right;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 8px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">1</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 8px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">2</li></ul></pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不过有时候我们对于自带的配色方案不太满意，那要怎么自己安装一些配色方案呢？主要分三步：</p><ol style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; list-style: none; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-size: 14px; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 0px 40px; list-style-type: decimal; word-break: break-all;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">在当前用户目录&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">~/</code>&nbsp;下的&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">.vim</code>&nbsp;目录(如果没有，<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">mkdir ~/.vim</code>进行新建该目录)。在&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">~/.vim/</code>&nbsp;下新建一个叫&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">colors</code>的目录，我们下一步下载的配色方案.vim文件便放到该目录下。</p></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 0px 40px; list-style-type: decimal; word-break: break-all;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">到一个配色网站上选择一个配色方案下载到&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">~/.vim/colors</code>&nbsp;目录下面。这里推荐一个非常好的网站:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bytefluent.com/vivify/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\">A ColorScheme Editor for Vim</a>, 这个网站不仅有很多的配色方案可供选择，还能自行进行编辑(比如变亮或变暗)再下载。比如我们看好了一个叫molokai的配色方案，点击下载按钮后下载 molokai.vim 的文件到&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">~/.vim/colors</code>&nbsp;目录下面&nbsp;<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all;\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/3E015071DB5495E4EC4B561E586C32BE.png\" alt=\"vivify\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; word-break: break-all; cursor: zoom-in;\" width=\"1278\" height=\"661\"></p></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 0px 40px; list-style-type: decimal; word-break: break-all;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all;\">修改&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">.vimrc</code>&nbsp;配置文件：<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border-radius: 2px; padding: 4px 2px 0px; word-break: break-all;\">colorscheme molokai</code>，退出再打开vim就能看到效果了。</p></li></ol><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注：网站上看到的配色方案效果仅供参考，不一定与实际使用的效果一样。</p><h3 id=\"使用插件安装\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a name=\"t1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>使用插件安装</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">vim插件：<a href=\"https://github.com/flazz/vim-colorschemes\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\">https://github.com/flazz/vim-colorschemes</a>，使用插件管理器进行快速安装，安装完成后直接设置即可。</p><h3 id=\"自己写一个-colorscheme\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 8px 0px 16px; font-size: 22px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 30px; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a name=\"t2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(78, 161, 219); cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\"></a>自己写一个 colorscheme</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">其实很简单，照葫芦画瓢即可，可以看我自己按照 spacemacs dark theme 修改的&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/liuchengxu/space-vim-dark\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\">space-vim-dark</a>&nbsp;colorscheme,</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"quiver-image-url/0D1E3477DCC21DFF2231903FB766C386.png\" alt=\"space-vim\" title=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; word-break: break-all; cursor: zoom-in;\" width=\"1280\" height=\"800\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">打开 colors 下面的 colorscheme, 其实很简单，完全可以自己写一个，主要内容差不多都是这样：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" name=\"code\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 8px 16px 4px 56px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 24px; position: relative; overflow-y: hidden; overflow-x: auto; font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border: none; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2;\"><code class=\"language-vim hljs vbnet has-numbering\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; display: block; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Consolas, Inconsolata, Courier, monospace; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; background-color: rgb(246, 248, 250); border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; overflow-x: auto; word-wrap: normal; word-break: break-all;\">hi <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 136); word-break: break-all;\">Function</span>        ctermfg=<span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 102, 102); word-break: break-all;\">134</span>   guifg=<span class=\"hljs-preprocessor\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 153, 0); word-break: break-all;\">#af5fd7 gui=bold            cterm=bold</span>\nhi Identifier      ctermfg=<span class=\"hljs-number\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 102, 102); word-break: break-all;\">98</span>    guifg=<span class=\"hljs-preprocessor\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(0, 153, 0); word-break: break-all;\">#875fd7 gui=bold           cterm=bold</span></code><ul class=\"pre-numbering\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 8px 0px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; word-break: break-all; position: absolute; width: 48px; background-color: rgb(238, 240, 244); top: 0px; left: 0px; text-align: right;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 8px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">1</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px 8px; margin: 0px; list-style: none; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">2</li></ul></pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">hi 就是 highlight，后面跟上一个类型，比如 Function, 就是指函数了，cterm 指的是 terminal 中的样式，比如加粗 bold，下划线 underline, gui 指的是 GUI vim中的样式，fg指的是 front ground前景色，bg 指的是 background 背景色, 基本就是如此了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">调教一番就能使用了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; font-variant-ligatures: normal; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">reddit 上也有一个关于创建 Colorscheme 的讨论：<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/vim/comments/7auw18/creating_your_lovely_color_scheme_vimconf2017/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; color: rgb(103, 149, 181); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; word-break: break-all;\">Creating Your Lovely Color Scheme</a></p>"
    }
  ]
}